{"entries": [{"content": "I just heard him try to say 'Spotify' and he called it 'Stopipy'. Oh geez...", "timestamp": 1781538569.8178184, "hash": "52e05ac725ad03b665353135cf125b6e6f175770b7ff6320fd5bf68eaeae1b7f"}, {"content": "He just asked if we should go to the 'Frood Coat'. I am losing my mind.", "timestamp": 1781538569.817845, "hash": "45d5666deb71a74667dfca2abdc4b4ae9e8ad95d594f88a230dfd1296dac1372"}, {"content": "He tried to explain his 'ODSD' today. I think he meant OCD and ADHD.", "timestamp": 1781538569.8178475, "hash": "dd192173eec27d0df846cfd56534787d224c45ebeba93c7ce60c30431d902dbd"}], "synced": 3}